-04-27T15:46:34.000Z","msg":"樓主會唔會寫埋青春電話物語or花與愛麗絲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T15:47:02.000Z","msg":"自膠，電幻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e85b4de68b67a47902381777548e5c7bb75d25b0","tid":2506919,"uid":89030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T15:49:27.000Z","msg":"四月物語都好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57e11903d2221774c67d615cf9e985cf0954c8e2","tid":2506919,"uid":11185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T15:52:25.000Z","msg":"樓主會唔會睇埋小說？睇既話分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者睇埋新戲最後一封信"}]}